# OBJECT::GET_DEFAULT_AMMO_FOR_WEAPON_PICKUP

## Summary
Returns the standard ammo you receive when collecting a weapon of the given type

## Parameters
* **PICKUP_TYPE** weaponPickupType

## Returns
* **INT**
